{\b0 \cf26 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Whether county board\rquote s zoning decision is legislative or quasi-judicial turns on whether board is enacting ordinance, in which case it is acting legislatively, or enforcing it, in which case it may be acting quasi-judicially; factors considered in determining proper classification of board\rquote s action include nature of challenge thereto and manner in which board went about making its decision.
\par 
}
}
}
